  • Safety with Auto ShutoffOur coffee cup warmer features a convenient timer shutdown function, offering a customizable range from 1 to 12 hours. This intelligent feature lets you relish your beverage without any concerns. Prioritize safety and efficiency in your daily routines with this thoughtfully designed mug warmer
  • Ample Heating PanelDesigned with a generous heating surface, our coffee warmer effortlessly accommodates a wide range of cup sizes. Enjoy the convenience of a larger heating panel that readily accommodates most cups, ensuring a snug fit and optimal warmth. This coffee cup warmer is suitable for glass cups, stainless steel cups, ceramic cups, milk cartons, etc. And using a flat or thin bottomed mug will give the best results
  • Includes CoasterOur desk coffee warmer complete with a complementary coaster that adds a touch of sophistication to your coffee nook.
